The room was very spacious with a lovely king size bed and nice toiletries, replenished daily.	The balcony had impressive views and was private, the suite was huge and very comfortable.	The rooms are very clean, equipped with large flat screen TV and complimentary internet.	The room itself was clean, the bathroom was very modern, and the views of the water/harbor were very pretty.	The bed was quite comfortable, but the A/C a bit noisy.